    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Match New Sound Lengths\r\n\r\nKaysha needs to make these three sounds match up in her timeline. However, they are all different measure lengths.\r\n\r\n- Main Beat = 4 measures\r\n- Piano Fill = 3 measures\r\n- Blip = 1 measure \r\n\r\nTo solve this, Kaysha needs to identify a common pattern where all tracks can loop and end at the same time.\r\n\r\n**Your task:** Use **pattern recognition** to figure out how often each sound needs to repeat so they all align, then use loops to build your code. Your final song should match the example exactly!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/11807806b213c8a710caceb0e699a406-image-1744235904248.png)",
